---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import FAQ from '../components/FAQ.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Pomeranian Age Calculator — Dog to Human Years"
  description="Calculate your Pomeranian's age in human years using our breed-size based formula. Accurate Pomeranian dog years to human years conversion for small dogs. Calculate free instantly — no login required."
>
  <section class="container-custom py-10 sm:py-16 md:py-24 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <span class="inline-block text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--text-faint)] px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-[var(--border-default)] mb-4 sm:mb-6">Breed Calculator</span>
      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4">Pomeranian Age Calculator — Dog to Human Years</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Pomeranians are lively, fluffy companions that pack a lot of personality into a small frame. As a small breed, they enjoy longer lives and slower aging. Our Pomeranian age calculator gives you their accurate human age.
      </p>

      <div class="card p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 mb-6" id="breed-calc-root">
        <form id="breed-calc-form" class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <label for="breed-name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-1">Your Dog's Name <span class="text-[var(--text-faint)]">(optional)</span></label>
            <input type="text" id="breed-name" class="input-base" placeholder="e.g. Buddy" maxlength="30" />
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            <div>
              <label for="breed-years" class="block text-sm font-medium text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-1">Years</label>
              <input type="number" id="breed-years" class="input-base" placeholder="0" min="0" max="40" required />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="breed-months" class="block text-sm font-medium text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-1">Months</label>
              <select id="breed-months" class="select-base">
                {Array.from({ length: 12 }, (_, i) => <option value={i}>{i === 0 ? '0 months' : i === 1 ? '1 month' : `${i} months`}</option>)}
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn-primary w-full justify-center text-base py-3">Calculate Human Age</button>
        </form>

        <div id="breed-result" class="hidden mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-[var(--border-default)] text-center" aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true">
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1">Your Pomeranian is equivalent to</p>
          <p class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)]" id="breed-human-age">—</p>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-[var(--text-secondary)] mt-2">human years old</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] mt-4" id="breed-stage"></p>
          <p class="text-xs text-[var(--text-faint)] mt-2" id="breed-expectancy"></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-center text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]">
        <a href="/" class="text-[var(--color-link)] hover:underline">← Back to main Dog Age Calculator</a>
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-5 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)]">Pomeranian Age FAQ</h2>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium mb-1">How old is my Pomeranian in human years?</h3>
          <p>Use the calculator above — enter your Pomeranian's age in years and months. The small breed formula provides the most accurate conversion.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium mb-1">What is the lifespan of a Pomeranian?</h3>
          <p>Pomeranians typically live 12-16 years. Their small size and good genetics contribute to their impressive longevity.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium mb-1">At what age is a Pomeranian considered a senior?</h3>
          <p>Pomeranians reach senior status around 11-12 years. Dental care becomes especially important in their senior years.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium mb-1">Do Pomeranians age differently than other breeds?</h3>
          <p>Absolutely. Pomeranians age about 15% slower than medium breeds. A 12-year-old Pom is roughly equivalent to a 65-year-old human.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-[var(--border-default)]">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4">Pomeranian Health & Aging Guide</h2>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          <p>Pomeranians are a small breed with an impressive lifespan of 12-16 years. As toy breed dogs, they age about 15% slower than medium breeds. A 7-year-old Pomeranian is about 47 in human years, and many Poms remain playful and energetic well into their early teens. Their long lifespan means they spend a greater proportion of their lives as seniors compared to larger breeds.</p>
          <p>Common health issues include tracheal collapse, luxating patella, dental disease, and congestive heart failure. Their small mouths often lead to overcrowded teeth and accelerated dental disease, which can affect heart and kidney health if untreated. Pomeranians are also prone to obesity, which puts extra strain on their tiny joints and trachea.</p>
          <p>Daily tooth brushing and professional dental cleanings are essential for Pomeranian longevity. Use a harness instead of a collar to protect the trachea. Senior Poms benefit from joint supplements, a warm environment (they chill easily), and regular cardiac screenings starting around age 10. Despite their small size, they need daily walks and mental enrichment to stay healthy.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-[var(--border-default)]">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3 text-center">More Breed Calculators</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2">
          <a href="/labrador-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Labrador Age Calculator">Labrador</a>
          <a href="/golden-retriever-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Golden Retriever Age Calculator">Golden Retriever</a>
          <a href="/german-shepherd-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="German Shepherd Age Calculator">German Shepherd</a>
          <a href="/bulldog-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Bulldog Age Calculator">Bulldog</a>
          <a href="/beagle-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Beagle Age Calculator">Beagle</a>
          <a href="/poodle-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Poodle Age Calculator">Poodle</a>
          <a href="/chihuahua-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Chihuahua Age Calculator">Chihuahua</a>
          <a href="/pomeranian-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Pomeranian Age Calculator">Pomeranian</a>
          <a href="/great-dane-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Great Dane Age Calculator">Great Dane</a>
          <a href="/husky-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Husky Age Calculator">Husky</a>
          <a href="/shih-tzu-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Shih Tzu Age Calculator">Shih Tzu</a>
          <a href="/border-collie-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Border Collie Age Calculator">Border Collie</a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-center text-[var(--text-faint)] mt-4">
          <a href="/dog-age-chart" class="text-[var(--color-link)] hover:underline" title="Dog Age Chart by Breed Size">View full Dog Age Chart</a> — or — <a href="/compare" class="text-[var(--color-link)] hover:underline" title="Compare Two Dogs Age">Compare Two Dogs</a>
        </p>
      </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://dogbreedage.com" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Pomeranian Age Calculator", "item": "https://dogbreedage.com/pomeranian-age-calculator" }
  ]
})} />

<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How old is my Pomeranian in human years?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Use the calculator above — enter your Pomeranian's age in years and months. The small breed formula provides the most accurate conversion."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What is the lifespan of a Pomeranian?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Pomeranians typically live 12-16 years. Their small size and good genetics contribute to their impressive longevity."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "At what age is a Pomeranian considered a senior?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Pomeranians reach senior status around 11-12 years. Dental care becomes especially important in their senior years."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Do Pomeranians age differently than other breeds?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Absolutely. Pomeranians age about 15% slower than medium breeds. A 12-year-old Pom is roughly equivalent to a 65-year-old human."
      }
    }
  ]
})} />

<script>
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
  const form = document.getElementById('breed-calc-form');
  const result = document.getElementById('breed-result');
  const haEl = document.getElementById('breed-human-age');
  const stageEl = document.getElementById('breed-stage');
  const expEl = document.getElementById('breed-expectancy');
  const multiplier = 0.85;
  const lifespan = [12, 16];
  const sizeLabel = 'small';

  form.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    const years = parseInt(document.getElementById('breed-years').value);
    const months = parseInt(document.getElementById('breed-months').value);
    if (isNaN(years) || years < 0) { alert('Please enter a valid age'); return; }
    if (years === 0 && months === 0) { alert('Age must be greater than 0'); return; }
    const total = years + months / 12;
    const ha = Math.round((16 * Math.log(Math.max(total, 0.083)) + 31) * multiplier * 10) / 10;
    const thresholds = { small: [0.5,2,4,8,12,99], medium: [0.5,2,4,7,11,99], large: [0.5,1.5,3,6,9,99], giant: [0.5,1.5,3,5,8,99] };
    const stages = ['Puppy','Teenager','Young Adult','Adult','Senior','Elder'];
    const t = thresholds[sizeLabel];
    let stage = 'Elder';
    for (let i = 0; i < t.length; i++) { if (total <= t[i]) { stage = stages[i]; break; } }
    haEl.textContent = ha;
    stageEl.textContent = `Life Stage: ${stage}`;
    expEl.textContent = `Life expectancy: ${lifespan[0]}-${lifespan[1]} years`;
    result.classList.remove('hidden');
    result.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
  });
});
</script>
